    "row": 3,
    "rowsha": "jFj7yxhov/Xnc+F4VpQe4VVdt+Fko7M1bK6+fwzAymM=",
    "originContent": "A memory system for Claude Code that remembers what matters and forgets what doesn't.",
    "translatedContent": "一个为 Claude Code 设计的记忆系统，记住重要的，忘记无关的。"
  },
  {
    "row": 4,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 5,
    "rowsha": "lR7GTMM3zAqvnZnIsrFEy15m6S/PY8nzenXxRU1vPnA=",
    "originContent": "## The Problem",
    "translatedContent": "## 问题所在"
  },
  {
    "row": 6,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 7,
    "rowsha": "TZ6GxEUlWMU34ALRfLlNeARvNLla6uUaeyGIC8yT4kk=",
    "originContent": "Claude Code forgets everything between sessions. Every time you start a new conversation, it's like talking to someone with amnesia. You end up repeating yourself:",
    "translatedContent": "Claude Code 每次会话之间都会忘记所有内容。每次开始新对话，就像跟一个失忆的人交谈。你不得不重复自己说过的话："
  },
  {
    "row": 8,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 9,
    "rowsha": "hDPLJrYIVV4h/F8+BBjLss93bKeY8S7c71gfDOs2GOs=",
    "originContent": "- \"We already tried that approach, it didn't work.\"",
    "translatedContent": "- “我们已经试过那个方法了，没用。”"
  },
  {
    "row": 10,
    "rowsha": "70+8+wlwcojOab1Vdwg3W39Qy4MFJjREjEFB0D9KugU=",
    "originContent": "- \"Don't touch the auth file.\"",
    "translatedContent": "- “别动认证文件。”"
  },
  {
    "row": 11,
    "rowsha": "ZyQOc29SLJXYI5lZ8JlX1qqYObhkgT1jH1v0NC636EY=",
    "originContent": "- \"I prefer tabs over spaces.\"",
    "translatedContent": "- “我喜欢用制表符而不是空格。”"
  },
  {
    "row": 12,
    "rowsha": "TYtIR0c6n4JGe+f915LazTgVOgKRFdPN/e86y2yhWrk=",
    "originContent": "- \"The client's name is Sarah, not Sara.\"",
    "translatedContent": "- “客户的名字是 Sarah，不是 Sara。”"
  },
  {
    "row": 13,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 14,
    "rowsha": "xTbdN0mkYrwYog0sZ20JZEP7hcvSkZv7yTYFyglhy3U=",
    "originContent": "This gets old fast.",
    "translatedContent": "这很快就让人厌烦。"
  },
  {
    "row": 15,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 16,
    "rowsha": "/Ty+QheMF0pm7mne/6GvwTT7o+VPHMxHsC/yWJoXlgs=",
    "originContent": "## What Total Recall Does",
    "translatedContent": "## 全忆的功能"
  },
  {
    "row": 17,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "KPOxwwxaKf9NTM2yaHZtuJrMmvHZ86JiuFzV1aAEpKw=",
    "originContent": "It gives Claude Code a notepad that carries over between sessions, but a *picky* notepad. Not everything goes in. Before anything gets saved permanently, it has to pass a simple test: **will this matter tomorrow?**",
    "translatedContent": "它给 Claude Code 一个跨会话携带的笔记本，但这是一个*挑剔的*笔记本。不是所有东西都能被保存。任何东西永久保存前，都必须通过一个简单的考验：**明天还会重要吗？**"
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "tP7Wv1dm6Gobpq8HbmZvhBanwmVqaI0irwCB3YIagHk=",
    "originContent": "A preference you'll have for months? Saved. A decision you made and why? Saved. The fact that you ran a test five minutes ago? Not saved. The system keeps itself clean so Claude isn't wading through junk to find what's relevant.",
    "translatedContent": "你几个月以来的偏好？保存。你做出的决定及原因？保存。五分钟前你做的测试？不保存。系统保持整洁，这样 Claude 不必在垃圾信息中翻找重要内容。"
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "8Cn7DTPwgC5TRYcpx6IHELZx2Ghn/Zy5V2CaSviu4ik=",
    "originContent": "## How It Works",
    "translatedContent": "## 工作原理"
  },
  {
    "row": 23,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 24,
    "rowsha": "MZg4+7wDTdBnWXr52nsyXBlmPVbCfPqk8Ijt+ibgm34=",
    "originContent": "Think of it like a kitchen with four storage areas:",
    "translatedContent": "把它想象成一个有四个存储区域的厨房："
  },
  {
    "row": 25,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 26,
    "rowsha": "Bwk0QcP0Pnrim9UGY873PIJK/PmOr0W0/cCyPJUMCdE=",
    "originContent": "**Counter** (`CLAUDE.local.md`): The stuff you reach for every day. Loads automatically, every session. Kept small on purpose, around a page of text.",
    "translatedContent": "**台面**（`CLAUDE.local.md`）：你每天都会用到的东西。每次会话自动加载。故意保持小巧，大约一页文本。"
  },
  {
    "row": 27,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 28,
    "rowsha": "3ihmdmrKdTWsM3Fa2Hw1g0ZvtDLajjDs9QKKgLwI4js=",
    "originContent": "**Pantry** (`memory/registers/`): Organized by category. Your preferences, key decisions, project details, people you work with. Claude checks here when it needs something specific.",
    "translatedContent": "**储藏室**（`memory/registers/`）：按类别组织。你的偏好、关键决定、项目细节、合作人员。Claude 需要具体信息时会查这里。"
  },
  {
    "row": 29,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "XRMKGfBrM+EWgG+PojcL9a1F/3mj624As4WX2aq8dmE=",
    "originContent": "**Daily notebook** (`memory/daily/`): Timestamped scratch notes from each day. Everything gets written here first. You decide later what's worth keeping permanently.",
    "translatedContent": "**每日笔记本**（`memory/daily/`）：每天带时间戳的草稿笔记。所有内容先写这里。之后由你决定哪些永久保留。"
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "YqE7RN1YmLo/UajO6mQbdDGJRl6PO4d7Dw/gNUvAEJo=",
    "originContent": "**Storage closet** (`memory/archive/`): Old stuff that's done or outdated. Still searchable, but never loaded automatically.",
    "translatedContent": "**储物柜**（`memory/archive/`）：已完成或过时的旧内容。仍可搜索，但不会自动加载。"
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "xEs8LN8ewSux4KMUZzElGyzjVQo4dWfT7teIZI/RmH4=",
    "originContent": "The key idea: **notes hit the daily notebook first, then you promote the keepers.** Claude doesn't get to decide on its own what's important enough to remember permanently. You do.",
    "translatedContent": "核心理念：**笔记先写入每日笔记本，然后你挑选需要保留的。** Claude 不会自行决定什么足够重要永久记忆，由你掌控。"
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
