  {
    "row": 128,
    "rowsha": "sX1EZJiR5DGoxDTt4XzaG0fx5h6Y35R5+0l6mqXGwXQ=",
    "originContent": "**When a session starts:** Claude gets a summary of open items and recent daily notes. This is the \"here's where we left off\" briefing.",
    "translatedContent": "**会话开始时：** Claude 会收到未完成事项和近期每日笔记的摘要。这是“我们停在哪里”的简报。"
  },
  {
    "row": 129,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 130,
    "rowsha": "4u1O+Em3SpqJ3mru0oVl1xz3P30/TXRbm+P1oGJwDNY=",
    "originContent": "**Before memory gets compacted:** A timestamp gets written to the daily notebook so there's a record. This one is silent. Claude doesn't see it, it's just bookkeeping.",
    "translatedContent": "**内存压缩前：** 时间戳会写入每日笔记本以作记录。这是静默操作。Claude 看不到它，仅作簿记。"
  },
  {
    "row": 131,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 132,
    "rowsha": "hSeqKwqr8ygQIUMt8SORlFU1S6QYPMNgaQf0zkJMF/w=",
    "originContent": "Both hooks fail safely. If something goes wrong, they don't block Claude Code from working.",
    "translatedContent": "两个钩子都安全失败。如果出错，不会阻止 Claude Code 正常工作。"
  },
  {
    "row": 133,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 134,
    "rowsha": "1Fg5i8HpkF+UU9RF5HiJ/fTd4Zo8RNO2eFKdS0LN2Y8=",
    "originContent": "Hooks use `$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR` (standalone) or `${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}` (plugin) to resolve paths. No transcript parsing. The PreCompact hook only writes a timestamp marker to the daily log. It does not read or parse conversation transcripts.",
    "translatedContent": "钩子使用 `$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR`（独立版）或 `${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}`（插件）来解析路径。不解析转录文本。PreCompact 钩子只写时间戳标记到每日日志。它不读取或解析对话转录。"
  },
  {
    "row": 135,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
